ansitions. These and other components also\naffect the morphologies of the sources, and lead to wavelength dependent\nchanges in the widths of the profiles.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 24 Sep 2010 00:27:13 GMT"}],"update_date":"2010-09-27"}
